---
import { ContactForm } from "../contact-form";
import { Card, CardContent } from "../ui/card";
---

<section class="relative bg-[#2c2c34] py-32">
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 z-0 h-full w-full bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#222229_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#222229_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:6rem_4rem]"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10container mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2 class="mb-3 text-5xl font-bold">Contacto</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-zinc-300 max-w-3xl text-balance mx-auto">
                No pierdas tiempo, solicita una cotización online o llámanos a
                nuestro número para recibir asesoría personalizada y soluciones
                que elevarán la seguridad y productividad de tus proyectos.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mx-auto mt-24 grid max-w-screen-xl gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
            <Card className="h-full">
                <CardContent className="p-6 h-full">
                    <ContactForm client:idle />
                </CardContent>
            </Card>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg bg-accent p-2">
                <Card
                    className="relative flex h-full p-0 overflow-hidden group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute z-10 w-[55%] h-full scale-125 bg-white blur-lg group-hover:w-2/4 transition-all duration-500"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute w-[55%] h-full right-0">
                        <img
                            alt="Placeholder 2"
                            src="/pexels-andrew-2312369.jpg"
                            class="object-cover h-full"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative z-10 flex h-full flex-col justify-between gap-6 p-6"
                    >
                        <p class="text-2xl">Email y Teléfono</p>
                        <div class="flex flex-col">
                            <a
                                href="mailto:informacion@oaklandtaller.cl"
                                class="hover:underline"
                            >
                                informacion@oaklandtaller.cl
                            </a>
                            <a
                                href="tel:+569 89 55 8951"
                                class="hover:underline"
                            >
                                +569 89 55 8951
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </Card>

                <Card
                    className="relative flex h-full p-0 overflow-hidden group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute z-10 w-[55%] h-full scale-125 bg-white blur-lg group-hover:w-2/4 transition-all duration-500"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute w-[55%] h-full right-0">
                        <img
                            alt="Placeholder 2"
                            src="/image.png"
                            class="object-cover h-full"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative z-10 flex h-full flex-col justify-between gap-6 p-6"
                    >
                        <p class="text-2xl">Nuestras oficina</p>
                        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-4">
                            <div>
                                <p
                                    class="mb-2 text-xl text-muted-foreground md:mb-4"
                                >
                                    Coquimbo, Chile.
                                </p>
                                <p>Av. Los talleres #1621, Galpón 14</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </Card>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
